01:02:43.630 --> 01:02:47.320
on the frequency limit of styli,
because there are sound systems

01:02:47.320 --> 01:02:50.470
that are capable of
reproducing beyond 4000 hertz,

01:02:50.470 --> 01:02:55.720
so is there a stylus
contractor for that sweet spot?

01:02:55.720 --> 01:02:58.710 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Olivia Dill: Yeah, I'm not sure--

01:02:58.710 --> 01:03:01.030
